{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为《欢乐英雄》第四十三回\"龙王庙\"，主要讲述郭大路追查神秘麻子的经历。郭大路在会宾楼观察麻子后跟踪至粮食坊，却发现自己被骗。麻子通过留春院妓女梅兰传话，约定三更在大明湖东龙王庙见面。郭大路前往龙王庙途中遭遇驼背老人和独脚和尚的阻挠，最终在庙中发现一名被绑架的十六七岁小姑娘。郭大路决定放弃追查麻子，先送小姑娘回家，展现了他善良正直的品格。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非他已发现了我在这里，乘机借尿遁了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你听明白了吗？只要你说实话，这串钱就是你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们家里是不是还有个麻子？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎么知道的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然能，他刚才进去，马上就会出来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他真的会出来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hai_zi",
      "speaker_name": "孩子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在他已经出来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要找的是那麻子，你以前难道没见过？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是不是那麻子告诉你的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你若能替我找到那麻子，我就天天去捧你的场。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_lan",
      "speaker_name": "梅兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说话不算数的是王八。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么话？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_lan",
      "speaker_name": "梅兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他说今天晚上三更时，在大明湖东边的龙王庙里等你，他还说……还说……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他还说什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mei_lan",
      "speaker_name": "梅兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他还说，你若是没胆子，不敢去也没关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "的兜",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你为什么不一直送我到门口？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tuo_bei_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "驼背老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为我这条老命还想再多活两年。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你送我到了那里，就活不下去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今晚有什么不同？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你只管放心送我去，你若死了，我……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你既不肯走，我也有腿，我难道不能自己走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "龙王庙是不是真的就在前面呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我姓郭，叫郭大路，大方的大，上路的路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我并未请教尊姓大名。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但我们能在这种地方碰到，总算是有缘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怎知我是碰巧遇见你的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你难道不是？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道你本就是特地来找我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "找我干什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要你回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "回去？回到哪里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从哪里来，就回到哪里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是不是想不让我到龙王庙去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那是个不祥的地方，去的人必然有祸事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你一定要去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，先击倒我，再从我的身上跨过去吧？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你是特地来找我打架的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好手法，就凭这一手，我就未必打得过你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_jiao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独脚人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你现在还来得及回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最多只砍断你一条腿，因为你只有一条腿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "打狗棒法",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你，饶了我吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是什么人，怎么会到这种地方来的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "求求你……饶了我吧……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你用不着求我，我可不是来害你的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 528
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那个什么人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把我绑到这里来的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我……我根本就没有看见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 542
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你是怎么来的呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 544,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你醒过来的时候，这里难道没有别的人？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里又黑又冷，我实在怕得要命，幸好总算在桌上摸到了块火石……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以你就将这里的灯全都点着了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嘤",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 619,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你用不着害怕，我送你回去。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 654,
      "line_end": 654
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "当然是真的，而且现在就可以送你回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是……你三更半夜到这里来，一定有很重要的事，你怎么能放下自己的事，送我回去呢了",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有所不为",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可以从后门进去，我住的屋子就在那边。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 700,
      "line_end": 700
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你最好换间屋子睡，最好找个年纪大的老妈子陪你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 702,
      "line_end": 702
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你怕什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 724
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
